Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,德古拉  前情提要\NPreviously, on Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是Ilona\NShe is Ilona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝不能再提\NYou must never again mention
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray长得像我妻子这件事\NMina Murray's resemblance to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,钢镍合金\NNickel steel alloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,困扰我们的问题得以解决了\NThe answer to our resonating casing problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一股东  帝国军火公司\NSole shareholder, empire munitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军收受贿赂\NGeneral Shaw is taking bribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你还乐于\NI didn't know you had such a remarkable penchant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁无辜男人的一生\Nfor ruining the lives of innocent men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你又怎能确定\NWhat makes you so sure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己不会遭此厄运？\Nthat you are immune from the same fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是会计\NShe's not a bookkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是个演员\NShe's an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我都按你的要求办了\NI did everything you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我促其进程\NI refined the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你终将行于日下\NYou will finally be able to walk in sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好长话短说\NMight I recommend keeping it short for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对血清时效一无所知\NWe have no idea how long the serum will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你和Grayson关系密切\NIf you are involved with Grayson
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他又真是吸血鬼\Nand he proves to be a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你将面对的是勃然大怒的兄弟会\Nyou will face the full wrath of the brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,女性有很多隐秘的方式传递爱慕\NWomen have many secret ways of expressing desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina可能对你有同样的感觉\NMina likely feels the same way about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你得离开了\NYou need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你找到了  - 德雷斯顿三联画\N- You found it. - The Dresden triptych.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\pos(184.533,53.446)\fs22}Grayson能源公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,成了 弄好了\NThere. Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家各就各位\NEveryone to their stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski先生 开始吧\NMr. Kowalski, fire it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,火力全开\NFull power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位\NGet to your stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你上一次吸血是什么时候?\NWhen did you last feed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,钢镍合金啊\NNickel steel alloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果连它也无法驯服这机器\NIf this doesn't tame the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就没东西可以了\Nnothing will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我  多久了\NAnswer me. How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这不该是你所应关心的  教授\NMy habits are not your concern, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在玩火自焚\NYou're playing with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己要什么\NI'm well aware of my needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我被他们折磨四个多世纪了\NI've been cursed with them for over four centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你需要血！  - 我并不饿\N- You need blood! - I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  我们准备好了\NGentlemen, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski先生  全力以赴啊\NMr. Kowalski, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样  先生们\NThat's it, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski先生\NMr. Kowalski,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,带他们去最近的公馆畅饮\Ntake these men to the nearest public house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我请客\NDrinks on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的先生! - 玩的开心 小伙儿们\N- Yes, sir! - And take it easy, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望公众展示那天\NI want this place shipshape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一切就绪\Nfor our public demonstration,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,随后日子里\Nand the day after that, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会证明自己\NI won't be worth a damn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而恶龙会将一无所有\Nand the Order Draco won't have a pot to piss in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker\NHarker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军是无辜的\NGeneral Shaw is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他从未收受贿赂推动战争\NHe never took bribes to promote war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的线人…\NBut your informant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个被收买了的演员\NMy informant was a paid actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会这样做？\NWho would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这骗局是精心设计的 - 嗯哼\N- The hoax was elaborate. - Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也需要谋划和资金\NThat takes planning and funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,无论谁做的  他们坐享其成\NWhoever did this, they sit to benefit from it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,金钱利益亦或是…\Nfinancially or at...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NIt was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别犯傻了\NDon't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很明确地告诉过你\NWas I not the one who told you explicitly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要放弃这桩生意的吗?\Nto drop the whole business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但你知道我不会\NYes, after you knew that I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不会那样做  你到底做了什么？\NThat I wouldn't.What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker  我们…只是做了必须做的\NWe, Harker, have done what was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一个值得尊敬的人名声被毁\NAn honorable man's reputation destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这有必要？\NThat was necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一个为能源战争倒下的卒子罢了\NJust another fallen soldier in the energy war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,前有古人  后还会有来者\NNot the first. Not the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我成了同谋\NYou've made me accomplice to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要揭发你\NI'll expose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,揭发我什么?\NExpose what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是你找到的那个会计\NYou were the one who sought out the bookkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把那些伪造的文件\NYou were the one who sent the forged documents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,发给报社\Nto the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我毁了他\NI didn't destroy the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NYou did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在  我们能言归正传了吧？\NNow, shall we return to the business at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我计划举办一次关于共振器的展会\NI'm planning a demonstration of my resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你给媒体发邀请函\NI need you to send out invitations to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗?\NWill that be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是好小伙儿\NThere's a good lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.2,104.059)\fn华文新魏\fs22\c&H0BE7EA&}Grayson无线磁能\N展演会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都看了这垃圾了吧?\NYou've seen this rubbish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须承认  他相当聪明\NWell, you must admit. He's quite clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天啊  - 怎么了？\N- Good God, man. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你还对他倾慕?\NAre you saying you admire the fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不  当然不是\NNo. Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是欣赏他玩的计谋\NOne just admires the game he plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他攻 我们就守\NHe thrusts, we parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson使我们一直处于防御状态\NGrayson keeps us on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来该换他防守了\NThen let's make him run for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在苏格兰警局里的人是谁\NOur man at Scotland Yard, Winthrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Morrow探长  先生\NChief Inspector Morrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做?\NWhat are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,做一些不太绅士的事\NSomething not befitting a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢  Winthrop - 是 先生\N- Oh, and Winthrop. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是时候把小Harker带来了\NPerhaps it's time we brought in Young Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你在布达佩斯要小心\NNow, you will be careful in Budapest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要需要\NIf you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以给你雇个保镖\NI can employ some bodyguards to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我更乐意依靠自己  先生\NI'm perfectly capable of defending myself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}这任务我只放心你去做\NI would not trust this task to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}在我父亲的城堡被洗劫一空\NAfter my father's castle was sacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}数百年的\Npriceless heirlooms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}家族珍宝遗失殆尽\Nthat had been in my family for centuries were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}我对此没什么留恋\NI would put a match to them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&}除了一样东西\NAll but one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield  把那画给我带回来\NRenfield, bring that painting back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H07F2DA&\fn华文行楷\fs22\4c&H901481&\pos(157.867,218.119)} 翻译: 小鱼  资本论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H07F2DA&\fn华文行楷\fs22\4c&H901481&\pos(252.8,265.168)}见习翻译：蜗小牛  句号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H07F2DA&\fn华文行楷\fs22\4c&H901481&\pos(230.4,221.683)}翻译 校对：幸福ing形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H07F2DA&\fn华文行楷\fs24\4c&H901481&\pos(203.733,88.376)}德  古  拉\N第一季 第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H07F2DA&\fn华文行楷\fs24\4c&H901481&\pos(204.8,236.654)}真 爱 字 幕 组\N——— 出 品 ———
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,把它带回去\NBring her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,四个小时\NFour hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的技术目前只能做到这样\NMy skills can afford you no more than that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  Abraham\NReally, Abraham?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,承认自己能力有限\NHow humble you are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你太谦虚了\Nto so readily admit your limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你风格啊\NQuite out of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的需求提升了  对吧\NIt is the improvement you demanded, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对现在来说已经足够了\NIt is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不吸血了\NWhy do you abstain from blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Markham小姐的血治好了我\NMiss Markham served to heal my burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在那后我还没吸血呢\NBut I have not fed since,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我从来都不该吸血\Nand perhaps I never shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的血清改变了我\NYour infusion has changed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉…重生了\NI feel...reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再世为人\NA man once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,自欺欺人\NYou deceive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么…可以治愈你的饥饿\NThere's no... cure for your hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远都是它的奴隶\NYou will always be its servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不做任何人的奴隶\NI'm servant to no man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐\NMiss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  - 今天早了五分钟\N- Oh. - Five minutes early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyayson先生\NMr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我吓到你了？\NDid I startle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我只是\NNo. I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿干嘛\NWhat in the world are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其他人一样\NSame as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,享受阳光\NSunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,难得的待遇\NIt's a rare treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吗\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  在阳光明媚的日子里\NYou know, it should be a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不微笑可是犯罪哟\Nnot to smile on so beautiful a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你愁什么呢\NSo, what's troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想说  我\NIf you'd rather not say, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  真的没事\NNo, no, it's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常帮我爸爸在医院巡房\NI was assisting my father on his rounds at hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们吵架了\Nand we had an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在皇家医院的生活单调无聊\NLife at Bethlem can be relentlessly bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,日子也枯索无味\NThe days can be so monotonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这种单调的生活\NWhat if that kind of tedium
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,影响他们的恢复怎么办？\Nhinders their recovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该跳跳舞\NThey should dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞  创造活力\NDance. Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,让血液跳动起来\NGets the blood pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好主意\NWhat an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会这么想\NHow did you ever think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢跳舞\NI like to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但我老爸不喜欢\NFather does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要一些令人信服的说法儿\NIt might take some convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我相信你具有说服力\NOh, I'm sure you can be very persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而且倔强\NAnd obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的缺点之一\NOne of my many flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你的缺点呢\NAnd yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前…\NA long memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会急躁\NImpatience...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而且嫉妒\NEnvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会想要拥有\NWhat could you possibly desire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你能随意得到的东西吗\Nthat is not already yours for the taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你收到了我的花\NI see you got my flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我按了门铃  但是没人回应\NI rang, but no one answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jenkins  - 你知道吗\N- Jenkins? - You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到从餐具厅传来的声音\NI heard some sounds coming from the pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,发现Jenkins先生正在看着你的厨子\NI found Mr. Jenkins seeing to your cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看着她？\NSeeing to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,急切的看着她\NVigorously seeing to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你扎到手了\NYou pricked your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下楼看看吧\NShall we go downstairs and watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上楼吧\NLet's go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NOh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  大白天和你滚床单  这…\NOh, to have you here in broad daylight, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有点颓废堕落\Nit's quite decadent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公\NIt's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他经常在庄园里\NHe appears to have gotten involved with the nurse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟照看他的护士纠缠不清\Nwho tends to him at our country estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,时有发生  无伤大雅\NThat happens. Harmless enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我先前也这样想  但是  额\NYes, that's what I thought at first, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这老笨蛋居然声称自己爱上了她\Nsilly old fool is claiming he's in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他真够厚颜无耻的\NHe's become quite brazen about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我该报复的   但是\NI would reciprocate, of course, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是对于他声誉的任何打击\NBut any damage inflicted upon his reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,都可能会转嫁到你身上\Nwould in turn be a strike against your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是进退两难\NIt's a quandary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\NTell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander  如果你是我\NWhat would you do in my position,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎么办\NAlexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找他的情人\NI'd go after the object of his affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾她…就是伤了他\NBy wounding her... you wound him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一场舞会  - 一场什么\N- A dance. - A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不符合常规\NI know it's unconventional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这太荒唐了\NThat's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是爸爸\NBut father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞会鼓励社交\Na dance would encourage socialization,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐有治愈的疗效\Nand music has such a power for healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,医院的所有病患\NThe men and women of this hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,住在单人间是有原因的\Nlive in separate wards for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,过去有过暴力事件\NIn the past there have been incidents of violence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不检点的行为  - 哦  上帝保佑\N- and indecent behavior. - Oh, God forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mina  - 爸爸\N- Mina. - Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些可怜人大多永远都不能回家\NMost of these poor souls will never return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经失去了自己简单快乐的生活\NThey have lost the simple pleasures of leading their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们难道不能稍微让他们\NCan we not give them one small reminder
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,回味下过往的生活吗\Nof the lives they've left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,医院财政可不会出一分钱\NNot a penny may come from the hospital budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,按指示向每个报社发送了邀请\NSent invitations to every newspaper as instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  这些是？\NExcellent. And these are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的拒绝信\NTheir refusals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,理由呢？\NWhat reason do they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是你\NYou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说你就是个卖万金油的\NThey say you're a charlatan peddling snake oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就如同P.T Barnum\Nlike P.T. Barnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,像P.T. Barnum\NLike P.T. Barnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要是他们想看马戏表演\NWell, if they want a circus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,爷给他们演一个便是\NI'm gonna give 'em one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对令他们难忘\NOne they won't soon forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H06F6E8&\fn华文新魏\pos(203.733,50.594)}Grayson无线磁电力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老少爷们都看过来！\NCome one! Come all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快来看壮观的电！\NCome see the magnificent electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,汲取于天地之精华！\NDrawn from the earth below and sky above!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您定会大开眼界！\NYou won't believe your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker 那好吧\NWell, then, Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们已是伦敦的焦点\NNow we have London's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不久我们将为世界所瞩目\NVery soon we'll have the world's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander 你病了吗？\NAlexander, are you ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想来是昨晚喝的有点高\NJust had a little bit too much to drink last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也许真是岁月不饶人\NPerhaps my age is catching up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天  - 那么\N- Goodness. - Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,运气好的话在这能碰到\Nthey should be there, with any luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们各就各位\NCome now, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在即将拍卖的是德累斯顿三联画\NThe Dresden triptych now come to auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要竞得这样一件15世纪的大师之作\NFor the 15th century's masterpiece
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从14万克朗起跳不算过吧？\NI think we can go higher than 140,000 coronas, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  夫人\NYes, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,15万\N150,000 coronas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有出17万5的吗？\NDo I have 175?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您了  夫人  非常感谢\NThere it is, madam. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有出二十万的吗吗？\NDo I have 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您了先生\NIt is yours, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,22.5万？\N225?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢夫人您的出价  25万有吗？\NI can see you, madam. 250?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,又是坐在后面的这位先生\NYes again, sir, in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有出27万5的吗？\NDo I have 275?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有？那好\NNo? Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,25万   成交\NClosing at 250,000 coronas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 女士们先生们…  - 100万\N- Ladies and gentlemen... - 1 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 你在说什么？\NDid you say, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我出一百万克朗 用英镑支付\N1 million corona. Payable in British sterling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的先生\NGood lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢问下\NDare I ask for 1 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有出110万的吗？\N100,000 coronas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就成交\NThen sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,德累斯顿三联画\NDresden triptych
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,100万克朗\Nfor 1 million coronas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这次换我惊到您了\NNow it's my turn to surprise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊\NAnd so you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在为明天的展示\NI was preparing my speech
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,准备演讲呢\Nfor the demonstration tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Harker不在这 - 是啊  呃\N- Harker isn't here. - No. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是过来跟您说两句的\NI came to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我？\NMe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 要是是这个情况\NWell, in that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我就得把演讲放放了\Nmy speech can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,您身体不适吗？\NAre you unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,您…你在出汗呢\NYou--You're perspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我身体再好不过了\NI've never been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 无须担心\NI assure you. No need for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您盛大的展示\NEveryone in London's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经在伦敦妇孺皆知\Nbeen talking about your big night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴设备成功修好了\NI'm glad the repairs were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,前排给你留了座位\NThere's a seat reserved for you at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好遗憾  我另有安排了\NUnfortunately, I have another engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 你知道吗\N- Hmm. - You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸同意在医院开一场舞会了\Nfather has consented to a dance at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那真好\NBrava.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你实在能说服别人啊  - 是啊\N- Persuasive, indeed. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 径直向您借留声机\NAnd I wonder, would it be terribly forward
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是否有几分冒昧？\Nif I asked to borrow your marvelous phonograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过是个小场合\NIt's quite a modest affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过没有伴奏就不能称其为舞会了\Nbut a dance isn't a dance without music,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是吗？  - 我会让人给你送去\N- is it? - I'll have it delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必为音乐这类小事操心\NYou shan't want for music. Or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我将如何能补偿你的慷慨大度呢？\NHow shall I ever repay such kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐 给我点时间\NGive me time, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信我会想出一个的\NI'm confident I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我敢肯定\NMy dear, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是误解了Mina的举动\Nyou must have mistaken Mina's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你错了\NNo. You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时不在那\NYou weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道究竟发生了什么\NI know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那究竟是怎么回事？\NAnd what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,厌恶  - 不\NRevulsion. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到的不过是恐惧\NWhat you saw was fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我了解她胜过我自己\NNo. You don't know her like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 也许我不知道\NNo, perhaps not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可我确实了解她这个类型\Nbut I know her type very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,软弱的小东西\NTimid little creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对自己的欲望畏首畏尾\NAfraid of their own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们俩…\NSee, you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她完全不是一类\NWe're a different breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们勇敢 我们诚实\NWe are brave. We are honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友 坦白说\NYour friend's behavior has been cowardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,懦弱到丑恶的地步\Nfrankly monstrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,的确丑恶 不是吗？\NIt was monstrous, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道她心肠歹毒？\NWho knew she had such venom in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她实在伤透了我的心\NTruly she's cut me to the very bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina是那么的聪明\NClever Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她懂那么多\NShe knows so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,却不懂痛苦为何物\NShe knows nothing of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还不如我了解得透\NNot as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,若她自己被爱人辜负\NHow would she feel to be let down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,又会怎么想呢？\Nby the one she loves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,被Jonathan辜负？\NBy Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在会是深刻的教训呢\NWell, that would be a terrible lesson, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 绝对的\NYes. Yes, it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说明晚要举办的盛会了吗？\NThis spectacle tomorrow evening, you've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然听说了\NOf course I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,局子里一半的小伙子\NHalf the boys of the yard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都要请假去\Nhave requested off to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Morrow探长\NChief Inspector Morrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,协会需要你的尽职尽责\Nthe Order requires your services
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谨言慎行\Nand your discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一期实验算是顺利\NInitial test holds steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都沿着正轨运行\NAll seems to be in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,写完演讲稿了吗？\NHave you written your speech yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kowalski  这条链子锈了\NKowalski, this roller chain's covered in rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看出哪锈了\NI don't see any rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你修就是！\NJust fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来不太对劲\NYou're not looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  若我是你\NI would tread very carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就会懂得分寸\Nif I were you, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的复仇任务\NThis evening our revenge rests
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可就全扛在你肩上了\Non your shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可你这肩膀\Nyet you look too weak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在连自己都撑不住\Nto shoulder your own garments!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你会复仇的\NYou will have your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁他们之后我们都会\NWhen we crush them, we both will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但对我来说更好的是\NBut the greater measure of mine is to defy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们在我身上下的诅咒也毁掉\Nthis blasted curse they've placed on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再杀人了\NI will not kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再去吸血\NI will not feed.、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做为一个人继续活下去\NI will live as a man
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然就去死\Nor not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是个处女吧\NYou're a virgin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过你调情\NI've seen you flirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无经验\NYou wear your inexperience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就像廉价的胭脂粉\Nlike a cheap rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说太绝情了\NNow you're just being cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  所有少女\NYou know, all young ladies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把自己打扮得像只孔雀\Npreen like peacocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想变成最引人注目\Nthinking that the loudest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,最闪亮的那个\Nand the brightest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才能吸引男人的目光\Nwill draw the man's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就连街头的妓女\NBut any streetwalker
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道用淫笑拉拢客人\Ncan simper and giggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会教你\NI will teach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如何抓住Jonathan的心\Nhow to haunt Jonathan's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一个女人的魅力\NYou see, a woman's power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不在于她的美貌和笑容\Nisn't in her beauty or her smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而是她的内在\Nbut in her mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对于你来说最有用的是\Nand the best application of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住Jonathan的五种感觉\Nwill be in capturing Jonathan's five senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,触觉\NTouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的指尖滑过他的肩膀\NYour fingertips across his arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,脸颊  和胸前\Nhis chest, his cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗅觉\NScent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天的记忆\NMemories of summer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让他回忆起夏天\Nreminding him of the warm sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,温暖的阳光\Non his naked skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听觉  你的笑声\NSound. Your laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,优雅轻盈\NLight and gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如同水晶做的铃铛\Nlike a crystal bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,视觉\NSight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,徘徊的眼神\NA look that lingers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎饱含承诺\Nand promises so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最后\NAnd finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,味觉\NTaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,巧妙地使用这些\NWield these blades wisely,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\Nmy dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan很快就可以被拿下\Nand Jonathan will be an easy kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  吓到你了小姐\NI am sorry to scare you, Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不需要打扫\Nbut no cleaning today, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是  对不起先生\NYes, sir. Beg your pardon, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.47,0:25:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大家下午好\NGood afternoon, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我为舞会准备了些花\NJust some flowers for the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.48,0:25:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy 这些真的没必要\NLucy, this is all very unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道在婚礼上\NI'm more than capable of choosing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿什么衣服\Nmy own wedding garments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.29,0:25:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道现在的小伙子\NI know the chaps
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.42,0:25:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,都会带乳色的手套\Nare all wearing ivory wedding gloves now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.12,0:25:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但巴黎的人都带薰衣草色\Nbut they're back to lavender in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.49,0:25:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你考虑的很周到\NYou seem well, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.06,0:25:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么周到了\NConsidering what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.73,0:25:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,前两天晚上\NThe other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina告诉我你很沮丧的原因\NMina told me why you were so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.44,0:25:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alistair\NAlistair.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.91,0:25:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOh, yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.41,0:25:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样最好\NIt's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.33,0:25:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他并不是我的菜\NHe wasn't exactly my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:25:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.78,0:26:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她还说了什么吗\NDid she say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.58,0:26:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没 怎么\NNo. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.12,0:26:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不 可怜的伙计\NOh, no, no, no. You poor lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来吧\NAllow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.13,0:26:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我来\NI insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.64,0:26:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.29,0:27:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜的馅饼\NPies fresh today!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.14,0:27:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早上新鲜的馅饼\NFresh this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.02,0:27:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,刚从烤炉出来的\NRight out of the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.39,0:27:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吗\NDo you mind if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.94,0:27:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 自便吧\NNo. Just go ahead. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.73,0:27:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜的馅饼  新鲜的馅饼\NFresh pies, fresh pies,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.80,0:27:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天新鲜的馅饼\Nfresh today!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.57,0:27:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 不客气\N- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.79,0:28:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来\NAllow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.53,0:28:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又回到远点了\NStart at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.37,0:28:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗\NAny trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.69,0:28:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么我控制不了的\NNothing I couldn't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.30,0:28:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你最爱的是什么\NSo who do you love most,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.79,0:28:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson\NAlexander Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.64,0:29:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray\NMina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.48,0:29:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽快回来\NI'll be back shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.57,0:29:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Harker 先生\NMr. Jonathan Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 我代表\N- Yes? - Come on behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.70,0:29:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning先生\Nof Mr. Browning...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.79,0:29:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在要跟你谈谈\NHe'd like a word with you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.21,0:29:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给我写信就可以了\NWell, a letter would have sufficed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.41,0:29:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我只是去参加\NAs it is, I'm just on my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.98,0:29:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,展示会  他知道\NDemonstration. Yes. He's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.21,0:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一会就好 可以吗\NHe asked but a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.61,0:29:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝呢\NAnd if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.08,0:29:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这会使这件事变得有点点麻烦 先生\NMake the task at hand a great deal messier, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.81,0:30:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐  Harker先生\NPlease remain seated, Mr. Harker,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.61,0:30:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然我们就要束缚你了\Nor we shall be forced to restrain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.25,0:30:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning先生\NMr. Browning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NCorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.68,0:30:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这\NI am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.22,0:30:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然 你断言是我\NAlthough, if you ever allege that I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.89,0:30:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我有四个可靠的证人\NI have four unimpeachable witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.22,0:30:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会一口咬定我现在\Nwho will testify under oath that I am at present
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.43,0:30:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在Gresham俱乐部用晚餐\Ndining at the Gresham Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.66,0:30:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么意思  为什么我在这\NWhat is this about? Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.56,0:30:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想把你介绍给我同事认识\NI merely wish to present you to my colleagues,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.77,0:30:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们目前还不能暴露身份\Nwho shall remain anonymous for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.90,0:30:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的同事  - 是的\N- Your colleagues? - Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.60,0:30:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 Harker先生\NWelcome, Mr. Harker,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.11,0:30:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来到龙之会\Nto the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.55,0:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,花园里的雏菊\NAnd with daisies from the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.34,0:30:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不用花一分钱\NNot a single penny was spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.92,0:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能与Chatsworth庄园舞厅比\NIt might not be the ballroom at Chatsworth
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.20,0:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但它本该如此\Nbut it should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.92,0:30:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是太令人钦佩了 亲爱的\NAdmirably resourceful, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.42,0:30:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生的留声机也会摆在这\NAnd Mr. Grayson's phonograph should be here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.06,0:31:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.19,0:31:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\NDo you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.44,0:31:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,受你邀请 Murray小姐\NAs you requested, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.98,0:31:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的音乐\NYour music.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.35,0:31:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray医生\NDr. Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.82,0:31:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我能邀请您跳支舞吗  女士\NMay I trouble you for this dance, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.94,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个房间里所有的人\NEvery man in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.06,0:31:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都已发过誓\Nhas sworn an oath
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.51,0:31:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他会因为上帝的旨意而牺牲自己\Nthat he will give up his life in order to serve God's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.65,0:32:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以做到吗  Harker先生\NAre you such a man, Mr. Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,愿与我们同舟共济\NAre you one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.65,0:32:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,作出牺牲吗？\NWould you make that sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,面对威胁  是的  坚定不移\NIn the face of a threat? Yes. Without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.89,0:32:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,至此之刻  威胁亦存\NEven as we speak, such a threat exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.03,0:32:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有一个异教徒\NAn ancient enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.33,0:32:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们知道此人是奥斯曼人\NThe heathens now known as the Ottomans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.00,0:32:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,奥斯曼帝国坐拥油海\NThe Ottomans sit on a sea of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.90,0:32:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能为英国等西方国家\NIf we do not secure those reserves for England
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.61,0:32:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,得到那些石油资源\Nand the West then soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.49,0:32:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那么很快  原油运输会被中断\Nvery soon, with the turn of the spigot,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.33,0:32:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有能力\Nthey will have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.46,0:32:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,使整个西部的工业停滞\Nto shut down Western industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.38,0:32:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们手无缚鸡之力的时候\Nand when we are defenseless
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.05,0:32:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会群起叛变摧毁我们\Ntheir hordes will rise up and crush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.65,0:32:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.69,0:32:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说句吗？\NIf I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.29,0:32:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请说\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.76,0:32:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果如你所言\NIf what you say is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.97,0:32:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么Grayson能源计划\Nthen Mr. Grayson's energy scheme
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.96,0:32:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,终会夺走奥斯曼人最厉害的武器\Nwill utterly strip the Ottomans of their greatest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.83,0:32:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有了电磁力  我们就不需要石油了\NWith geomagnetic power, we'll have no need for oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.24,0:33:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson的技术就完全没有用武之地了\NGrayson's technology is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.54,0:33:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要引起骚乱  事态发展下去\NA distraction, and if it continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.18,0:33:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,结果必然一败涂地\None that may prove deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.38,0:33:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让一个满嘴胡说\NWe cannot afford to be led astray
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.25,0:33:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,时刻想填满自己腰包的人\Nby a latter-day pied piper whose interests begin
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.19,0:33:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们带偏了\Nand end with lining his own pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.99,0:33:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们应该去阻止他  - 但是\N- It is our duty to stop him. - But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你的协助\NWe need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.89,0:33:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们让我做叛徒吗\NYou'd have me play Judas?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.33,0:33:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是  去搬倒这个伪救世主\NTo bring down a false messiah, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报\Nand in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你得到的权力和人脉\Npower and connections that would ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.17,0:33:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可助你和Murray小姐坐享美好未来\Nthe brightest of futures for you and Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.91,0:33:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我们吧   Harker先生\NJoin us, Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.01,0:33:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,协助我们  赢得这神圣的一战\NHelp us to win this Holy War once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.63,0:34:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会现在就要走了吧\NYou're not leaving already.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.96,0:34:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我要去展会\NForgive me. The demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.13,0:34:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉Harker  那里见\NTell Harker I'll see him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.80,0:34:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但一个小时后展会才开始\NBut it doesn't start for another hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.90,0:34:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且Jonathan还没来  虽说他答应会来\Nand Jonathan's not here, although he promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.24,0:34:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你很轻松\NI'm sure you'll have no
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.34,0:34:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就能再找到一个舞伴\Ntrouble finding another partner to dance with.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.58,0:34:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,近在眼前嘛\NI already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.94,0:34:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐  人们会议论你的？\NMiss Murray, what would people say?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.51,0:34:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看到吗？\NWhat people?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.72,0:35:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我跳支舞吧\NDance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.65,0:35:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生  这边走  - 我们到了\N- There you go, sir. - Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.32,0:35:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是给您的\NAnd one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是您的  先生  还有夫人您的\NThere's one for you, sir, and you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.12,0:35:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢  这个给您  先生\NThank you very much. And one for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.03,0:35:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在哪儿？  - 我想他们给我的衣服\N- Where is he? - I think they gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.87,0:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不合身  - 他在哪儿？\N- the wrong one. - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.71,0:36:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见他们这么开心  多亏了您\NI've never seen them so happy, and all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.42,0:36:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢你就够了\NThey only have you to thank for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.02,0:36:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有你照拂  花儿都会开的格外美\NWhy, any flower would blossom under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.13,0:36:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您抬举我了\NYou flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.93,0:36:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这让你不好意思了吗\NDoes that make you uncomfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.03,0:36:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.77,0:36:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我是不是该闭嘴了\NShould I stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.21,0:36:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.37,0:36:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手\NYour hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,您的手在发抖\NYour hands are trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.56,0:37:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.68,0:38:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.05,0:38:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  才是问题\NNothing. That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.28,0:38:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的老板临阵脱逃了\NYour boss is a no-show.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.12,0:38:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们  先生们  我们有理由相信\NLadies and gentlemen, we have reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这个机器会威胁到公共安全\Nthat this machine is a threat to public safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.50,0:38:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请大家从出口\Nso if you'll all please move towards the exit
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有秩序地离场\Nin an orderly fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.14,0:38:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们  先生们  撤离此处\NLadies and gentlemen, move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.82,0:38:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  女士们  先生们\NQuick as you can, ladies and gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.22,0:38:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,关了机器  把它封起来\NShut it down! Pack it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.86,0:38:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要没收这些东西\NI want all this confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.43,0:39:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人财产！  你无权干涉！\NThis is private property! You have no right!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.00,0:39:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这机器放这里没几天\NNext door there are over a hundred souls sick as dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.20,0:39:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,附近就有一百多人病得不轻\Nnot days after this infernal machine was constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.67,0:39:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不可能！\NThat's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.11,0:39:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这机器绝无健康隐患\NThis poses absolutely no health risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.11,0:39:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去和那个妈妈解释吧\NTell that to the mum with the baby in her arms
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.47,0:39:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子还在她怀里吐着血呢\Nwho's spittin' up blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.08,0:39:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然  你是拿了别人的钱\NClearly you're not above being paid for your services,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.98,0:39:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,无论谁给的  我给你双倍价格\Nso how much to double whoever's paid you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.92,0:39:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放开你的脏手！\NGet your damn hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.75,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,滚！\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.15,0:39:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,走开！\NGo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.36,0:39:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！  快！\NCome on! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.70,0:39:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,往前走  快  快\NCome along! Move. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.47,0:39:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.09,0:40:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我该陪你的\NI know I should have been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.72,0:40:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,带我回家\NTake me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.80,0:40:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul\NPaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.83,0:40:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul！\NPaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该收下那些钱\NYou should have taken the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.74,0:40:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.81,0:41:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小“酌”一口去了？\NOff for a little lip, were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.88,0:41:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你相比  这算得了什么\NMy savagery pales in comparison to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.39,0:41:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应把我拉回那个\NYou won't drag me back into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.37,0:41:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,唾弃我的世界\Nthat had forsaken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.39,0:41:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是你  拿血清忽悠我\NYou, who cheated me with the vaccine
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.56,0:41:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让我体验那种\Nthat gives me but the taste of the life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.84,0:41:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,绝无可能过上的生活的滋味\NI can never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.43,0:41:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是你  给了我希望\NYou, who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.94,0:42:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我更像怪物\NYou're more of a monster than I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.08,0:42:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有朝一日\Nand someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.94,0:42:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为此杀了你\NI will kill you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.17,0:42:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
